<p>

<FONT color=black size=4 
  face=Arial>[Download tool]</FONT></p>
<p align="justify"><font face="Arial" size="4">Option 1: Standalone Executable 
Files (For users who do not have permission to install new software on 
computers, e.g. in labs, library and so on) </font></p>
<ul>
	<li>
	<P align="left"><FONT 
  face=Arial>Student Tool &amp; Chronobot Cute Client: Click<a href="zipfile/cvc.zip"> Here</a> to download a zip file of the tools. It 
  includes two executable files: </FONT></P></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
	<blockquote>
		<P align="left"><FONT 
  face=Arial>cvcStudentTool.exe and cvcChronobot.exe.</FONT></P>
	</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<ul>
	<li>
	<P align="left"><FONT 
  face=Arial>&nbsp;Teacher Tool (for testing only):Click<a href="zipfile/teacher.zip"> Here</a> to download a zip file of the tools. It 
  includes two executable files: </FONT></P></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
	<blockquote>
		<P align="left"><font face="Arial">cvcTeacherTool.exe and 
		cvcInfoCenter.exe</font></P>
	</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<P align="left"><font face="Arial">All tools work on MS windows 9X/2000/XP. Please save them to disk. 
  Make&nbsp; shortcuts on desktop if you like.</font></P>
<P align="justify"><font face="Arial" size="4">Option 2: Installable Version:</font></P>
<ul>
	<li>
	<P align="justify"><font face="Arial" size="4">&nbsp;</font><FONT 
  face=Arial>Student Tool: Click <a href="zipfile/cvcStudentAll.zip">here</a> to 
	download a zip file. It includes an installation file:</FONT></P></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
	<blockquote>
		<P align="justify"><font face="Arial">cvcStudentAll.exe</font></P>
	</blockquote>
	<P align="justify"><font face="Arial">Run it, and follow the instructions. 
	It will install the student suite including communication tool, chronobot 
	cute client, configuration tool, and live update.&nbsp; </font></P>
</blockquote>
<ul>
	<li>
	<P align="justify"><font face="Arial">Teacher Tool : Click
	<a href="zipfile/cvcTeacherAll.zip">here</a> to download a zip file. It 
	includes an installation file:</font></P></li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
	<blockquote>
		<P align="justify"><font face="Arial">cvcTeacherAll.exe</font></P>
	</blockquote>
	<P align="justify"><font face="Arial">Run it, and follow the instructions. 
	It will install the teacher suite including communication tool, information 
	center, configuration tool, and live update.&nbsp; </font></P>
</blockquote>
<p><FONT face=Arial size=4>[Startup]</FONT></p>
<BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">
  <P dir=ltr><FONT 
  face=Arial>Make sure your computer is connected to the Internet before you 
  execute the files.</FONT></P>
  <ul>
    <li dir="ltr">
  <P dir=ltr><font face="Arial">Virtual Classroom:&nbsp; Please run cvcStudentTool.exe. 
  Once it starts, you will be asked to input your first name, last name and 
  password. Your password is the one you provided during the online registration. </font></P>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <ul>
    <li><font face="Arial">Chronobot: Please run cvcChronobot.exe. Once it 
    starts, you will be asked to input your username and password. Your username 
    is your last name +first letter of your first name. The password is&nbsp; 
    the same as above.&nbsp; </font></li>
  </ul>
  <blockquote>
  <P dir=ltr><FONT 
  face=Arial>For example:</FONT></P>
  <BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr style="MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">
    <P dir=ltr><FONT 
    face=Arial><U>First Name&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
    Last Name&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
    </U></FONT></P>
    <P dir=ltr><FONT 
    face=Arial>james&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;bond&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></P></BLOCKQUOTE>
  <P><FONT face=Arial>The username is 'bondj'. </FONT></P>
  </blockquote>
  <P><b><FONT 
  face=Arial>Attention: Please use the name which you registered online.&nbsp;All 
  names should be in <font color="#FF0000">lower</font> case.</FONT></b></P></BLOCKQUOTE>
<p><FONT face=Arial><FONT color=black>
<img border="0" src="troubleshooting.jpg" width="40" height="40"></FONT><font size="4" color="#800000">Troubleshooting: 
